org.linqs.psl.config

Class Options

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.linqs.psl.config.Options

  • public class Options
extends Object
    The canonical place to keep all configuration options. Options.fetchOptions() can be used to fetch all the options dynamically. The main() method will collect all the options and write them out to stdout as JSON.
